      </h2>

      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl font-sans text-[0.98rem] font-light leading-relaxed text-white/75">
        Prime-time and divisional games book out fast once the NFL schedule drops.
        Lock in your flat-rate ride now and update details closer to game day.
        Dispatch is staffed 24/7. A human answers every call.
      </p>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-stretch justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4"
        role="group"
        aria-label="Book Seahawks game day transportation"
